title: Vince Wilfork on Tom Brady not having a "dog in the fight": "That's bullcrap"

sources.name: Pro Football Talk
sources.title: Vince Wilfork on Tom Brady not having a "dog in the fight": "That's bullcrap"
sources.description: On Monday, former Patriots quarterback Tom Brady said of the Seahawks-Patriots matchup in Super Bowl LX: "I don't have a dog in the fight."
